Text: This is a great record. Arne Nordheim is a contemporary composer who experimented with electronic music in the sixties. This record is performed by Biosphere who is a original and verys skilled ambient/electronica performer from the arctic city of Tromso. Deatprod has made many noise albums, and have worked closely with Motorpsycho. You can buy the album here: http://www.runegrammofon.com/artists/biosphere/rcd2005-biospheredeathprodnord
